des:
New technology comes to the old school as Palmyra Racing Association is now Alexa enabled. We you can learn all about when we are racing and a bit of our history. Try phrases like:
"Alexa, ask Palmyra Racing Association what's going on this year"
or 
"Alexa, ask Palmyra Racing Association when theyre racing again"
